./my-claw/sdp/prd-cost-tracking.md:82:| CT-012 | **Budget reset scheduling.** Implement reliable budget period resets: daily at midnight UTC, weekly at Monday 00:00 UTC. Clear degradation flags, reset spend counters in Redis, archive the completed period's totals to PostgreSQL. Handle edge cases: missed resets (server was down), timezone changes, leap seconds. Send a "budget reset" confirmation to Telegram. | MUST | T1 | - Daily reset at midnight UTC<br/>- Weekly reset at Monday 00:00 UTC<br/>- Missed resets caught up on next run<br/>- Degradation flags cleared on reset<br/>- Confirmation sent to Telegram |
