my-claw/sdp/prd-server-optimization.md:31:| OPT-002 | Expand Redis usage beyond metrics. Move these to Redis: (a) conversation history cache — last 50 messages for instant retrieval during routing, (b) agent prompt cache — cache the AGENT_CONTEXT + recent conversation to avoid rebuilding per request, (c) model fitness scores — cache Observatory skill scores with 5-min TTL for fast selector queries, (d) pet status cache — current pet stats for instant /pets responses. Use Redis key prefixes: `claw:conv:`, `claw:prompt:`, `claw:fitness:`, `claw:pet:`. | SHOULD | T2 | - Conversation history in Redis with 50-message cap<br/>- Agent prompts cached and reused<br/>- Fitness scores cached with TTL<br/>- Pet stats cached<br/>- All reads from Redis, writes to both Redis + persistent store |
