my-claw/sdp/prd-gap-analyzer.md:48:| GA-005 | Create `gap_analyzer/completion_verifier.py` — for every task with status "complete", run tiered verification: (1) file existence — does every file mentioned in the task description exist? (2) import check — does `python -c "import module"` succeed? (3) behavioral check — do the key classes/functions mentioned exist and have the right signatures? Mark tasks that fail verification as "needs_review" with a detailed failure reason. | T2 |
